  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. \"7 times a number <math><mi>y</mi></math>\" is <math><mn>7</mn><mi>y</mi></math>. \"4 less than\" means subtract 4, giving <math><mn>7</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></math>. Setting this equal to 52 gives <math><mn>7</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>52</mn></math>.</p><p>Choice B switches the operation. Choice C swaps coefficients. Choice D rearranges incorrectly.</p>",
